AnimalSocialAerodynamics.lean — Laws of animal distribution and formation flight.

This module formalizes the laws of group behavior and energy efficiency:
1. Distribution: The Ideal Free Distribution (IFD) and input matching.
2. Formation: Aerodynamics of V-formation and vortex-upwash exploitation.
3. Efficiency: Power reduction and range extension in collective flight.
